[Fonds-Verrettes is a commune in the Croix-des-Bouquets Arrondissement, in the Ouest Department of Haiti. It is the highest elevation town in Haiti. It can be found on a map at http://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fonds-Verrettes. A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map is available at https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=3331226,9574. - Mod.LL]
